{"tid":334048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓91歲慰安婦逝世 倖存者僅剩37人","createTime":"2017-07-24T11:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T00:05:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c96b4f5659b8fb61dfe9f735968e8f44e4ec18a8","tid":334048,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:18:57.000Z","msg":"2017年7月24日 星期一<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170724/s00005/7dfde783e18748780eef8ad3517d31d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170724%2Fs00005%2F7dfde783e18748780eef8ad3517d31d8.jpg&h=8571ac5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國京畿道一名受害慰安婦逝世，享年91歲。據悉，韓國外交部藏部長官康京與多名韓國政府官員打算出席該名女士的葬禮。<br />\n其他報道：【姊妹花藏屍案】日警拘涉棄屍男子　曾光顧死者打工餐廳<br />\n韓聯社報道指，該名女士姓金，17歲被日軍強徵爲慰安婦，期間被帶到中國吉林，此後三年間曾經7次試圖自殺不遂。該名女士去世後，韓國政府登記備案的238名慰安婦中，倖存者僅剩37名，年齡80歲至90歲不等。<br />\n慰安婦問題一直纏擾日韓的關係發展，雖然兩國於2015年簽署《日韓慰安婦問題協議》，承諾不再於國際場合就慰安婦問題互相批評，然而文在寅上任後推翻協議。本月初，韓國政府打算將慰安婦相關文獻申報列入《世界記憶名錄》，並在首爾興建慰安婦博物館，日本外相岸田文雄就此表示強烈抗議。<br />\n（中新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170724/s00005/1500872087669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170724%2Fs00005%2F1500872087669&d=QwmHDIQMkF5p0IdhLXjCG9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=7aaaa714\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170724%2Fs00005%2F1500872087669&h=9f7a429e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170724/s00005/1500872087669</a>"},{"pid":"8adaaab4e1addcce6f43c0e9f10e78ceb6659f25","tid":334048,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b015cf5570d618e13a5377821a4c4de0c3332f98","tid":334048,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T13:33:21.000